column8: 入学日
column9: Enrollment Day

column8: 启程日，钥冢细雨霏霏。在这里埋下你的墓碑、姓名和誓言。
column9: On this day of departure, a gentle drizzle falls over the Keygrave.\nHere, you shall bury your tombstone, your name, and your oath.

column8: 古老的伦蒂尼恩夜雾弥漫，在昏黄路灯无法照亮的角落，黑暗正伺机而动。
column9: Mist shrouds the ancient city of Londinium, and darkness lurks where the dim streetlights fail to reach.

column8: 欢迎来到热情好客的拉伊小镇——冬夜的犬吠会让每位来访者宾至如归。
column9: Welcome to the hospitable town of Rye—where the barking of dogs on winter nights makes every visitor feel at home.

column8: 与“歇斯底里”的刻板印象相悖，此处是静止的无声世界。
column9: Contrary to the stereotype of "hysteria," this is a still and silent world.

column8: 风暴之眼
column9: Eye of the Storm

column8: 陌生的船只，陌生的少女，陌生的敌人。飘摇于大海之中，等待着调查员们的，是一场与命运的抗争……
column9: A strange ship; a strange girl; and strange enemies. Adrift upon the sea, what awaits our investigators is a struggle against fate...

column8: 群星落入深海，在海底闪烁着无人能解读的愿望。
column9: Stars fall into the abyss, shimmering with wishes that no one can decipher.

column8: 勒姆瓦希，卡达斯中部地带的黄沙之国。在被当地人称为“圣河”的母亲河哺育下，名为亚兰的文明正在暗中滋长与消亡……
column9: Remouahe, a desert nation located in central Kadath.\nNurtured by the "Holy River," the Aram civilization quietly rises—and quietly, it fades away...

column8: 入场。静坐。等待。渴求。\n指挥棒轻轻扬起。准备好，聆听这宇宙最深邃的隐秘了吗？
column9: Enter. Sit. Wait. Yearn.\nGently, the baton rises. Are you ready to listen to the deepest secrets of the universe?

column8:
祂做了一场漫长的梦。
祂梦见神与星辰，梦见尘埃衍化文明，文明化为尘埃。
祂梦见恨与爱，梦见欢愉与恐惧。 
祂从睡梦中惊醒。梦境中的一切，从未存在。
column9:
It had a long dream.
It dreamed of gods and stars; of dust giving rise to civilization, and of civilization returning to dust.
It dreamed of hate and love; of joy and fear.
It woke with a start. Everything in its dream—had never existed.

column8: 被灰雾埋葬的旧日废都\n跨越无光的星辰，与无上意志的碎念在毁损维度重逢
column9: Buried in the gray mist lies the ruins of an ancient city.\nTraverse the void of lightless stars, reuniting with the fragmented thoughts of the Supreme Will in a damaged Dimension.

column8: 群体潜意识构筑的疗养院\n在这里，躯壳的消解并非终点，心灵的死亡才是终结。\n踏入者啊，请保持理智，人性是你穿行心灵迷宫的唯一依仗。
column9: A sanatorium constructed by the collective subconscious.\nHere, the dissolution of the shell is not the end; the death of the mind is.\nThose who enter, please maintain your sanity. Your humanity shall be your only recourse as you traverse the maze of your mind.

column8:
欢庆吧，我的朋友♪
月光下的骸骨悄然绽放，一位挚爱被送上餐盘♪
所有的宾客都已到来！唱呀，跳呀♪
我们从不为亡灵祈祷，我们从不为尸首哀悼♪
她将记忆交予了我，她将眼泪交予了我♪
让我们咽下她的魂灵与腐肉♪
在死亡的盛宴中，我们再度重圆♪
column9:
Rejoice, my friend♪
Beneath the moonlight, bones quietly bloom♪
My beloved lies still on a silver plate♪
All the guests have arrived! Sing! Dance!♪
We never pray for the dead, we never mourn the corpses♪
She gave me her memories, she gave me her tears♪
Let us swallow her soul, her decaying flesh♪
In this feast of death, we are reunited once more♪
